{
  "stem": "10587.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we were not-- we-- you did not-- you were not able to lie down to sleep.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You had to sit like packed in herring, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the facilities were limited.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were not enough bathrooms and not enough-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was a shortage of everything because they-- they bunched in so many people to this camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- but one of the group, and one of the brothers from-- from the butchers, worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They got to-- they were assigned to the kitchen and cooks, and they were able to bring some food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was helping out the rest of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had to be very careful because people, if they knew that you had food on you, the Russians or the gypsies, they would stab you at night and take it away from you.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- so I used to walk around and-- we never worked in-- in this camp-- this was only a camp to be redistributed or to be whatever they-- they were planning to do.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- How long were you in Gross-Rosen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too long, not too long at all, a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Gross-Rosen, we-- we were sent on an open rail, you know, rail-- railroad cars-- cattle-- real cattle cars and no roof.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we-- we was sent to a few camps, I think, where-- and they used to pull us over on the side, and we used to stand there for a day or two because their wehrmacht had the first priority to-- to go through.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- we were sent somewheres to a camp where they didn't have the room for us, and we were parked outside of Dresden.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
